Whenever You make use of Your Digital Key You also agree that (a) Digital Keys can only be used when Bluetooth functionality is enabled on Your mobile phone or device and (b) Digital Keys can only be issued to or deleted from Your mobile phone or device when Your mobile phone or device has network connectivity (e.g., 3G, 4G or wireless Internet connectivity).
